name: ThatCarbonOffset
description:
Thatcarbonoffsetcompany will be a collection of farms using regenerative farming to maximize carbon capture and restore ecosystems.
Verified carbon credits will be sold directly from our projects, using TCO tokens, to reinvest in more farms to restore the carbon balance. The TCO ecosystem is planned to include our own carbon credit exchange, NFT auction site all using the TCO token for those who want to contribute to the global fight against climate change by reducing or eliminating their carbon footprint.
